729406f-a.title: Richmond: Richmond Road - Tysens Lane
729406f-a.text:
Richmond Road, south side, between Tysens Lane
nnd Wilder Avenue, showing ''Cedar Villa,'' the home of H.
Charles Miller (1925). It was owned by A.E. Crute in 1917
and by John McCarthy in 1907 and 1898. Dates refer to maps
on which the names of the owners appear.
July, 1925
P. L. Sperr
wo REPRODUCTIONS
